That would be very helpful.

00:44:29.430 --> 00:44:30.730
Give it whatever you want.

00:44:30.730 --> 00:44:32.112
I don't care about the ratings.

00:44:32.112 --> 00:44:33.570
I care that it gets
read and people

00:44:33.570 --> 00:44:35.730
have real comments on it.

