00:44:53.110 --> 00:44:54.570
So it's about gratitude.

00:44:54.570 --> 00:44:55.370
Can you see that?

00:44:55.370 --> 00:44:56.880
It's about gratitude.

00:44:56.880 --> 00:44:59.820
And for some people, that
